===Definitions===
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[resist]], to [[oppose]]
#: {{zh-x|抗日.戰爭|"War of '''Resistance Against''' Japan" (the {{w|Second Sino-Japanese War}})}}
#* {{zh-x|關公 曰：「汝 怎 敢 抗 吾？」禁 曰：「上命 差{chāi}遣，身不由己。望 君侯 憐憫，誓 以 死 報。」|{{w|Guan Yu|Lord Guan}} said: "How dare you '''oppose''' me?" {{w|Yu Jin|(Yu) Jin}} said: "We were ordered from above, (we did so) not on our own accord. We hope ye, milord, would have mercy. We swear we'll repay that with death."|ref=Sanguo Yanyi}}
# {{lb|zh|obsolete}} to [[raise]]; to [[lift]]; to [[elevate]]; to [[hold]] [[high]]
#* {{zh-x|大-侯 既-抗，弓-矢 斯-張。|The great target '''is set up''';<br>The bows and arrows are made ready for the shooting.|ref=Shijing}}
#* {{zh-x|卑-溼、重-遲、貪利，則 抗 之 以 高-志。|The self-deprecating people, the encumbered and sluggish, and the pettily covetous ones — we '''elevate''' them with a high spirit.|ref=Xunzi}}
#* {{zh-x|寧{nìng} 與 騏驥 '''@亢'''-軛 乎？將{jiāng} 隨 駑馬 之-跡 乎？|Shall I rather '''hold myself aloft''' in the yoke of Pegasus, or waste away after the tracks of a Rocinante?|ref=Chuci}}

